Auto generate thankyou cards for Christmas / Birthday / Bar Mitzvah gifts.

Can pull colour scheme from colourlovers.com API.

Available fonts:
- Courier
- Helvetica
- Times-Roman
- Symbol
- ZapfDingbats
- Courier-Bold
- Courier-Oblique
- Courier-BoldOblique
- Times-Bold
- Times-Italic
- Times-BoldItalic
- Helvetica-Bold
- Helvetica-Oblique
- Helvetica-BoldOblique

Available border styles:
- Circles
